 Galvatron saw the emp missle comeing at him. He put his hands togeather and 
fired a 5 foot energy blast denenateing it before it reached them. The 
explosion was minor not makeing and sever damage to Galva or megastrom. 
Guiledart returned to the bunker.
      "Sir the bombs have been given. Unless he has a rndomly changeing 
sheild frequency wich I scanners say is negative this should creat a hole for 
at least 15 seconds. But my time may be off. So we must get in very close 
range before we throw them. It will give us damage but it will be worth it. 
All we need now is darkefate to confirm the pan and we are set."

--part1_a2.1093e1ef.27cada93_boundary
